    "type": "refactor",
    "subject": "Replace dirsExcluded with filesExcluded in FTP.scandir method",
    "body": "The FTP.scandir method is responsible for scanning a directory recursively and adding the files and directories to the appropriate lists based on the include and exclude patterns. The changes made in this commit replace 'dirsExcluded' with 'filesExcluded' to focus on files instead of directories.\n\nThe replacement of 'dirsExcluded' with 'filesExcluded' will change the behavior of the function by adding files to the excluded list instead of directories.\n\nThis commit does not introduce any new features or functionality, but it refactors an existing part of the codebase."
}

