    "type": "feat",
    "subject": "Added setRepositoryRegistry method to MavenRepositoryProvider",
    "body": "This commit adds a new method, setRepositoryRegistry, to the MavenRepositoryProvider class. This method is used to set the repository registry, which is used to look up repositories by name. The repository registry is an instance of RepositoryRegistry that contains all the repositories in the system.\n\nThe added method takes a RepositoryRegistry object as a parameter and sets it as the repository registry for the MavenRepositoryProvider instance.\n\nThis change is necessary because it allows other components of Archiva (such as ArchivaCli) to use this provider without having access to all repositories in the system."
}

