    "body": "This commit refactors the AccessTokenService class by replacing duplicate code with a single call to OAuthUtils.injectContextIntoOAuthProvider method. It also adds a log statement to handle exceptions while creating the access token and injects the message context into the OAuth providers using OAuthUtils.injectContextIntoOAuthProvider method."
